Description:
You find yourself on the main deck, surrounded by ghostly sailors moving about as if they are still tending to the ship. 

Some are cleaning and polishing the deck, while others are preparing the tattered sails for a new journey. 

They seem oblivious to your presence and don't appear to be a threat. Perhaps they might even be willing to share some information if you ask them.
